paojiangdou chau roumou 泡豇豆炒肉末


INGREDIENTS:

1 Bunch Longbeans
150g Minced Pork
5 Star Anise
1Tbsp Sichuan Peppercorns
240g Salt for Pickling
5g Salt
40g Rock Sugar
5g White Sugar
1 Head Garlic, whole
2 Cloves Garlic, Sliced
10g Ginger, minced
150g Fresh Chilies
8 Dried Chilies
1.5L Water
1.5 Tbsp Soy Sauce
1.5Tbsp Shaoxing Wine
1/4tsp White Pepper



DIRECTIONS:


PICKLING: 

Add to Jar:
Star Anise
Sichuan Peppercorns
240g Salt 
40g Rock Sugar
30g Garlic
150g Chilies
1 Bunch Longbeans
1.5L Water

Wait 10 days


MISE:

In a bowl combine
	150g Minced Pork
	1tsp Soy Sauce
	1/4tsp White Pepper
	1tsp Shaoxing


1Tbsp Soy in Mise Bowl
1Tbsp Shaoxing in Mise Bowl
1tsp Sugar in Mise Bowl
1tsp Salt in Mise Bowl
Snip Dried Chilis
Peel & Slice Garlic
Peel & Slice Ginger
Slice Pickled chilis
Rinse longbeans
Dice longbeans


STIR FRY:

Long Yau
Add Garlic Slices
Sichuan Peppercorns 
Ginger
Dried Chilis
Pickled Chilis 
Fry until fragrant
Add Ground Pork
Fry Until Golden
Add 1Tbsp Shaoxing
Fry until reduced
Add Longbeans
Add 1tsp sugar
Add 1tsp salt
Add 1Tbsp soy
Fry for 2-3min
Serve